---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Customer Stories — Formic"
  description="Mid-market CPG operators running Formic systems every day. Land O'Frost, Mi Rancho, Mariani Family, Taffy Town, and more."
  ogTitle="Customer Stories"
  ogDescription="Proven on real production floors."
>
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://formic.co/stories" slot="head" />

  <style is:global slot="head">
.stories-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:1px;background:var(--lgrey);max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto}
.story-card{background:var(--white);padding:36px 36px 40px;display:grid;grid-template-columns:200px 1fr;gap:32px;text-decoration:none;cursor:none;transition:background .25s,transform .35s cubic-bezier(.2,.6,.2,1);align-items:center;position:relative}
.story-card:hover{background:#e8ede9}
.story-photo{position:relative;width:200px;height:200px;overflow:hidden;background:var(--black);flex-shrink:0}
.story-photo img{width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;display:block;transition:transform .8s cubic-bezier(.2,.6,.2,1),filter .4s ease;filter:brightness(.82) saturate(.92)}
.story-card:hover .story-photo img{transform:scale(1.05);filter:brightness(.95) saturate(1)}
.story-fpo{position:absolute;top:10px;right:10px;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,.78);background:rgba(0,0,0,.45);backdrop-filter:blur(8px);padding:3px 7px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.18);z-index:2}
.story-photo-overlay{position:absolute;left:14px;bottom:14px;display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:8px;color:var(--white);z-index:2}
.story-photo-overlay::before{content:"";position:absolute;left:-14px;right:-14px;bottom:-14px;top:-32px;background:linear-gradient(to top,rgba(9,21,23,.8),transparent);z-index:-1}
.story-ct{font-family:var(--sans);font-size:48px;font-weight:500;color:var(--orange);line-height:1;letter-spacing:-.02em}
.story-ctlbl{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,.78)}
.story-body{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px}
.story-name{font-family:var(--sans);font-size:22px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:-.015em;color:var(--black);margin-bottom:2px}
.story-challenge{font-size:14px;color:var(--mgrey);line-height:1.65;margin:0}
.story-win{font-size:14px;font-weight:400;color:var(--black);line-height:1.65;margin:0}
.story-win::before{content:"→ ";color:var(--orange)}
.story-arrow{position:absolute;right:32px;bottom:32px;font-family:var(--sans);font-size:22px;color:var(--orange);transition:transform .25s ease}
.story-card:hover .story-arrow{transform:translateX(6px)}
@media(max-width:900px){.stories-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}.story-card{padding:24px;grid-template-columns:140px 1fr;gap:20px}.story-photo,.story-photo img{width:140px;height:140px}.story-ct{font-size:36px}.story-name{font-size:18px}.story-arrow{right:24px;bottom:24px}}
  </style>

<div class="detail-bc">
  <a href="/">Home</a><span class="sep">/</span>Customer Stories
</div>

<section class="detail-hero">
  <div class="si">
    <div class="slabel" style="color:var(--orange)">Customer Stories</div>
    <h1>Proven on <em>real floors</em>.</h1>
    <p class="lede">CPG operators who run Formic systems every day. Names you know — and the outcomes they actually saw on the floor, written down so you can compare.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white" style="padding:96px 80px">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:0">
    <div class="db-tag">Every deployment</div>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:clamp(36px,4vw,60px);font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.02em;line-height:1.05;color:var(--black);margin:8px 0 32px">Two dozen floors. <em style="color:var(--orange);font-style:normal">One playbook.</em></h2>
    <div class="stories-grid">
      <a href="/stories/land-o-frost" class="story-card">
        <div class="story-photo">
          <img src="/stories/land-o-frost-hero.jpg" alt="Land O'Frost gantry palletizing" loading="lazy"/>
          <div class="story-photo-overlay"><span class="story-ct">5</span><span class="story-ctlbl">Palletizers</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="story-body">
          <div class="story-name">Land O'Frost</div>
          <p class="story-challenge">Manual palletizing of 128,000 lbs/day was the hardest job on the floor.</p>
          <p class="story-win">5 gantry palletizers in 2 weekends → ~20% lower labor OpEx</p>
        </div>
        <span class="story-arrow">→</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/stories/mi-rancho" class="story-card">
